{"tid":2390010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北角封區餐廳被發強檢告票 徐英偉指封區範圍應自知需檢測","createTime":"2021-02-01T09:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T01:14:28.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1d51de73cb2273ea96823a5646997b54e0bb074e","tid":2390010,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"北角封區餐廳被發強檢告票 徐英偉指封區範圍應自知需檢測<br />\n<br />\n北角東發大廈日前封區檢測期間，有餐廳員工不滿全晚無被安排檢測，但翌日被發強檢告票。民政事務局長徐英偉回應時指，不只東發大廈，所有處於封區檢測範圍的人士，都應該知道需要在時限內檢測，如果無完成就是違法，強調之後亦會繼續巡查及嚴厲執法。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2377294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2377294&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=cc60f6b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2377294</a>"},{"pid":"dd92dedb131473de033e4c779ea5d9df04810c64","tid":2390010,"uid":88663,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，嗰時就唔好叫人等啦咁"},{"pid":"821872062728d10765a9a4691c7947bee7d56028","tid":2390010,"uid":47210,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老味, 主動出嚟問你班撚樣幾多次都係耍人返去等通知㗎喇, 北角係咁, 麗港城又係咁, 終於就係唔撚肯認錯, 千錯萬錯都係香港市民錯<br />\n<br />\n<code>寧化飛灰\n不作浮塵\n光復香港\n時代革命</code>"},{"pid":"b4b72dc29869b6af7fccbc6090a97868a0d03e65","tid":2390010,"uid":103325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:35:00.000Z","msg":"咁點解有麗港城居民落去問幾時檢測，但職員又叫佢返上樓等嘅"},{"pid":"99997b287826966873087ed93de0f11d54057817","tid":2390010,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"全世界都唔戴底褲口罩 係得你個衰仔表忠"},{"pid":"8ff21c29b95a0389cfd2ae73efadb1a8d17c1435","tid":2390010,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:38:43.000Z","msg":"又spin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji